sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Unregistered User
    participant FE as React<br/>LandingPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>PlanListView
    participant SER as SubscriptionPlanSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Click "View Plans"
    FE->>API: GET /api/subscriptions/plans/
    API->>DB: SubscriptionPlan.objects.all()
    DB-->>API: QuerySet[SubscriptionPlan]
    API->>SER: SubscriptionPlanSerializer(plans, many=True)
    SER-->>API: Serialized plan data
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {plans: [...]}
    FE-->>U: Render pricing cards (Free / Premium / Exclusive)
    U->>FE: Click "Get Started" on selected plan
    FE-->>U: Navigate to RegisterPage with plan pre-selected
